{"type": "article", "id": 16292, "title": "M2Malletier 春夏手包系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-20T06:30:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000345VcwzeBgyifp5h7dU.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是 M2Malletier 推出的新款手包，这个品牌是由哥伦比亚的两个女生 Melissa Losada 和 Marcela Velez 自创的。她们热爱使用金属杆的手把，与皮质包对比，极简而有个性。新款更大胆采用不同颜色与形状的材料，给女生的穿搭提供不同选择。另外，皮质本身的花纹也让皮包有了质感，不会因极简而显得无聊。<a href=\"http://www.m2malletier.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是她们的主页。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143634pkbd7v0QPHh1fas8.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143635BUuCT4f8gd6p5FOP.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261436353Y1kjGVyPlvgeIU8.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143636kGQw29YxA8M3qlEO.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143636Ywb0PClxUN2dErWK.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261436370hiRLcXBnwyPVkGp.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143637lZ5uTxhs496mnPYU.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\